  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Battle of Summerfield</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\nBefore <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Summerfield\" title=\"Summerfield\">Summerfield</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\">Durrandon</a> victory</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">Stormlands</a> army</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a> army</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/20px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/30px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/40px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> King <a href=\"/index.php/Argilac_Durrandon\" title=\"Argilac Durrandon\">Argilac Durrandon</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\"><img alt=\"House Gardener.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/20px-House_Gardener.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/30px-House_Gardener.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/40px-House_Gardener.svg.png 2x\" /></a> King <a href=\"/index.php/Garse_VII_Gardener\" title=\"Garse VII Gardener\">Garse VII Gardener</a> †</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Unknown</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\"><img alt=\"House Gardener.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/20px-House_Gardener.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/30px-House_Gardener.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/40px-House_Gardener.svg.png 2x\" /></a> King <a href=\"/index.php/Garse_VII_Gardener\" title=\"Garse VII Gardener\">Garse VII Gardener</a> †</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>Battle of Summerfield</b> was a battle between the forces of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\">House Durrandon</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">Stormlands</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\">House Gardener</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a> which took place before <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Garse_VII_Gardener\" title=\"Garse VII Gardener\">Garse VII Gardener</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Reach\" title=\"King of the Reach\">King of the Reach</a>, was killed by the <a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">Storm King</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Argilac_Durrandon\" title=\"Argilac Durrandon\">Argilac the Arrogant</a> during the battle.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_of_Summerfield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Reign of the Dragons: The Conquest.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403115744\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.070 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.257 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 229/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 9176/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7438/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 937/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 691/5000000 bytes\nLua time usag